data.description: Are you ready to make this beautiful ranch your new home! This ranch features a open concept feel with the living room and kitchen opened to each other for great entertaining. The first floor welcomes you with 3 bedrooms and a full updated bathroom. Also for your entertainment needs there is an awesome partially finished basement that has lounge area and a room that could be used as a potential office, playroom, or potential bedroom. Newer updates throughout the home with some of the updates being a new hot water tank, new paint throughout house and basement, bathroom, etc. So come take a look and fall in love with this beautiful ranch that is ready for you to call home!
